{"tid":1721763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到葵涌邨手足比人拉 有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-11-14T17:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T17:56:56.000Z","uid":1598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"191d4133c4ebf036a97e1d4568472cecb7703a09","tid":1721763,"uid":1598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:53:21.000Z","msg":"小弟係嗰頭都住咗十幾年<br />\n由之前集體屌白卡到前幾日食TG反抗<br />\n見到大家嘅變化都幾開心<br />\n但係我一直覺得唔應該係葵涌邨set rb<br />\n地形上嚟睇 葵涌邨比三條行車路圍住<br />\n無論邊一條都好近屋邨 <br />\n啲狗上到嚟可以好快就包抄到<br />\n加上葵涌邨比葵芳同新界南狗屋圍住<br />\n絕對唔係一個好嘅據點<br />\n而葵涌邨手足好多都係街坊同細路<br />\n見到綠狗落地就即刻跑走<br />\n有經驗嘅人得好少 甚至唔足以守住防線<br />\n做法唔完美 可接受 要改善<br />\n我<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔建議</strong></span></span>大家改為十點圍屌狗宿舍<br />\n到時見到綠狗就好走喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfd42d5951f01d1f6f081e28924f27838632451","tid":1721763,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:54:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去retweet like reply</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Twitter吹大雞！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">！！！McConnell支持法案，重點推 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1195006159679299584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1195006159679299584&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc64aGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=aca5177e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1195006159679299584&h=8c1d25b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1195006159679299584</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Rick 多謝 McConnell <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1195011922799804416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F